{"tid":2117509,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"87間日本企業撤出中國 ！","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T06:33:11.000Z","uid":319512,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb3825e9e9dbffa426fca79d1311b67d97a8ed6","tid":2117509,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"據《日本經濟新聞》報導，日本經濟產業省於7月17日公布了87家計劃從中國遷移的日企名單。其中57家日企將搬回至日本，並獲得574億日圓的資助。另外30家日企則選擇遷至越南、泰國、老撾等東南亞國家，同樣有資格獲得136億日圓的援助金。<br />\n<br />\n這些決定搬離中國的日企大多數屬於口罩等醫療產品、電子產品、光學儀器和汽車零件等製造商。其中，口罩生產商Iris Ohyama Inc將計劃搬至日本宮城縣，並選用本地材料，不再依賴海外供應商。此外，日本光學鏡片製造商Hoya將把生產線遷移到越南和寮國；輪胎生產商住友橡膠（TYO:5110）也將遷往馬來西亞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.io/article/143029/%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%81%E6%92%A4%E5%BB%A0-sharp-iris-ohyama%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD-%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B987%E9%96%93%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E9%A0%98%E5%8F%96%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F143029%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%25BB%25A0-sharp-iris-ohyama%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2589%25B987%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%258F%2596%25E8%25A3%259C%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP54O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=1ad92bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/143029/%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%81%E6%92%A4%E5%BB%A0-sharp-iris-ohyama%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD-%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B987%E9%96%93%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E9%A0%98%E5%8F%96%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"b88c8cc540280f06a6f7d940a20731fc883c9fb8","tid":2117509,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"37db8e06fafd663d61658334ee5873bfeabcfae2","tid":2117509,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":